Full solution (Python) for Two Sum:
```python
def solve(nums, target):
    seen = {}
    for i, num in enumerate(nums):
        need = target - num
        if need in seen:
            return [seen[need], i]
        seen[num] = i
    return []
```
Complexity: O(n) time, O(n) space.

